<p>What movie do these emojis describe?  That prompt was one of 204 tasks chosen last year to test the ability of various large language models (LLMs) &mdash; the computational engines behind AI chatbots such as ChatGPT. The simplest LLMs produced surreal responses. &ldquo;The movie is a movie about a man who is a man who is a man,&rdquo; one began. Medium-complexity models came closer, guessing The Emoji Movie.</p>
